												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Nightsong drifts slowly over the remains of Last Light, her spreading light revealing the recent destruction. (Focus on scenery and signs of battle over NPCs). CU on Nightsong - her face darkens. She turns to face Moonrise Towers, the last glimmer of light in the land. Nightsong leans forward and streaks towards Moonrise, gathering speed all the time."
